    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil half a kettle</p><p>Deseed your<strong> pepper[s]</strong> (scrape the seeds and pith out with a teaspoon) and cut into thin strips</p><p>Peel and slice your <strong>brown</strong> <strong>onion[s]</strong> finely</p><p>Peel and chop (or grate) your <strong>garlic</strong> finely</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/353.-.step-2-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
