            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of<strong> olive oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the<strong> pepper strips </strong>and<strong> sliced onion</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>sugar</strong>, then cook for 7-9 min or until softened</p><p>Once softened, add the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>garlic</strong> and cook for a further 1 min</p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/353.-.step-3-x200.jpg",
