      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, dissolve your <strong>vegetable stock mix<span class=\"text-danger\"> </span></strong>in 200ml<span class=\"text-purple\"> [300ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[400ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong>, then stir in <strong>half</strong> of your <strong>chipotle paste </strong>(not a fan of spice? Just add a little!)</p><p>Drain and rinse your<strong> cannellini beans</strong></p><p>Add your<strong> vegetable stock</strong> and <strong>drained</strong> <strong>cannellini</strong> <strong>beans</strong> to the softened pepper and onion and cook for 10-15 min over a low heat or until reduced to a thick stew</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
