          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>mayo </strong>in a small bowl with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong>, <strong>remaining chipotle</strong> <strong>paste </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!), a drizzle of<strong> olive oil</strong> and <strong>half</strong> of the <strong>chopped</strong> <strong>coriander </strong>(save the rest for garnish!)</p><p>Season with a pinch of <strong>pepper</strong> and set aside – this is your <strong>smoky mayo</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/353.-.step-6-x200.jpg",
