    {
      "instruction": "<p>Stir the <strong>remaining</strong> <strong>chopped coriander </strong>through the <strong>stew</strong>, then top with the <strong>fried eggs </strong>– this is your <strong>tapas-style pepper, bean & egg stew</strong></p><p>Serve the <strong>tapas-style pepper, bean & egg stew </strong>with the <strong>crispy potatoes </strong>and <strong>smoky mayo</strong> to the side</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
